captions.text: This week's Music Monday is going to be K-pop related but not a Kpop review.
We've done almost a hundred and fifty different Kpop Music Mondays and we've talked about A Lot of bands.
But we realized that don't necessarily know the names of all the members of the bands.
YES, I KNOW, WE ARE EVIL PEOPLE, OK?
The point is: today we're going to be doing a Kpop Member Name Showdown.
SooZee is basically going to name a group and we're going to go back and forth
and name the members within a group.
Whoever can name the most members within a group is going to win 1 point.
Whoever has the most points at the end of the showdown will be the winner.
If you're playing with a friend you can play the same way that we're playing.
But if you're going to play alone, you want to give yourself one point for every single member that you name.
And at the end of this video we're going to give you a Kpop Master Of The Universe Ranking System
Ok, Kai-Bai-Bo* to go first [*equivalent of Rock-Paper-Scissors]
